<div class="row" id="otherversions"> <!-- Alternate Versions Heading -->
  <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12">
    <h2 class="section-title">Alternate Versions of ClamAV</h2>

    <p class="gray">Various third parties have developed versions of ClamAV to work on a variety of operating systems.
      Several of these are listed below. Installation instructions for many operating systems can be found in
      the <a class="gray" href="/documentation">documentation</a>.</p>

