<div class="row section version" id="dwn-solaris"> <!-- Solaris Versions -->
  <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12">
    <h5 class="gray">Solaris Signatures</h5>

    <div class="panel-group" id="accordionSolaris">
      <div class="panel panel-link"> <!-- collapseOpenCSW-->
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h4 class="panel-title">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordionSolaris" href="#collapseOpenCSW"><span class="red">OpenCSW</span></a>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseOpenCSW" class="panel-collapse">
          <div class="panel-body">
            <p>OpenCSW is a community software project for Solaris 8+ on both Sparc and x86. It packages more than 2000
              popular open source titles and they can all easily be installed with dependency handling via pkgutil which
              is modeled after Debians <em>apt-get</em>.</p>

            <p><code># pkgutil -i clamav</code></p>

            <p>More info on <a href="http://www.opencsw.org/" class="red" target="_blank">OpenCSW</a> can be found on
              their website.</p>
