          </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseEleven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
          <div class="panel-body">
            ClamSMTP is an SMTP filter for Postfix and other mail servers that checks for viruses using the ClamAV
            anti-virus software. It aims to be lightweight, reliable, and simple rather than have a myriad of options.
            Written in C without major dependencies. | get
            <a class="blue" href="http://thewalter.net/stef/software/clamsmtp/">ClamSMTP</a>
