        </div>
        <div id="collapse18" class="panel-collapse collapse">
          <div class="panel-body">Smtp-gated is a transparent SMTP proxy supporting: NAT on Linux (netfilter), NAT on
            FreeBSD (ipfw and others getsockopt-compatible), or dedicated mode (separate/external machine). DATA traffic
            is spooled in write-thru mode and then scanned for viruses or spam. The program is transparent for TLS
            connections. | get <a class="blue" href="http://software.klolik.org/smtp-gated/">SMTP-gated</a>
