<div class="row section-lines" id="submittools">
  <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
    <h2 class="section-title">Submit ClamAV Tools</h2>

    <p class="gray">If you have written software that can make use of ClamAV, please notify the
      <a class="blue" href="mailto:sfcommunity@cisco.com" target="_top">Community Manager</a>. Be sure to include the
      name of the program, a short description, the URL of home site, and the author's email address. Please note that
      we will only review software that is released under an OSI license.</p>
